<h1 class="mb-3">Transport Logistics Optimization Application</h1>
<p>This application assists the transport dispatcher by automating the assignment of orders to drivers.</p>

<h2 class="mt-5">Modules</h2>
<ul>
    <li><strong>Drivers</strong> – displays a list of drivers, the number of assigned deliveries, and the number of possible orders.</li>
    <li><strong>Orders</strong> – displays orders in a printable card format, including details and the assigned driver.</li>
</ul>
